{"tid":533253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"證實誤發飛彈警報　夏威夷色情網瀏覽量突激增","createTime":"2018-01-18T14:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T19:02:17.000Z","uid":31255,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"caa0d69d84eff2fce776673c4f5ca0e362f3a752","tid":533253,"uid":31255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180118/640_db635db4dda68bcd6ebb6cb5980354a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180118%2F640_db635db4dda68bcd6ebb6cb5980354a9.jpg&h=07b80a80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國夏威夷上周六(13日)誤發導彈來襲警報，一度引起民眾恐慌，隨後夏威夷危難管理局立即澄清是一次「誤警」。全球最大成人網站《PornHub》表示，在警報發佈後，來自夏威夷的瀏覽量較平常少了77%，但當局澄清是場誤會後，瀏覽量隨即急速上升，較平常高出近50%。<br />\n<br />\n《PornHub》表示，在當天上午8時7分發佈警報後的20分鐘內，來自夏威夷的流量較正常大幅下跌77%，網站相信，因為民眾都在努力尋找庇護所，「沒時間瀏覽網站」。直到8時45分，管理局在《推特》(twitter)上澄清「夏威夷沒有導彈威脅」後的16分鐘，網站流量立刻急速上升，到9時01分時達到高峰，較平常高出近50%。<br />\n<br />\n當時導彈來襲警報造成民眾恐懼、壓力上升，許多司機丟下汽車，逃往附近隧道躲藏，有髮廊業者向顧客發短訊，取消所有預約，並表示全天不營業。當民眾確認誤報後，可能都需要抒發壓力，而登入成人網站似乎是很多人的「熱門選擇」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180118/1281471/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180118%2F1281471%2F&d=L6KZPOph35KrJKR2XHuAkywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5ad6161d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180118%2F1281471%2F&h=970eb7b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180118/1281471/</a>"},{"pid":"d1aa620eff7f74295df8762df6a76115368a3322","tid":533253,"uid":73722,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"quote":{"pid":"caa0d69d84eff2fce776673c4f5ca0e362f3a752","tid":533253,"uid":31255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180118/640_db635db4dda68bcd6ebb